       title: "Uni Kuru Toga Mechanical Pencil - 0.5 mm - Kiki's Delivery Service", price: "$2.00", text: "A perfect gift for fans of Studio Ghibli and Hayao Miyazaki, this pencil features a design inspired by the classic animated film Kiki's Delivery Service!"},


